}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== *Enterprise AR9344 560Mhz CPU *IEEE 802.11ac compliant and backward compatible with 802.11abgn *Up to 26dBm 2.4G & 24dBm 5G output power *IEEE 802.3af/at PoE *Data rates of up to 867Mbps in 802.11ac 80 MHz channels *Built-in 4dBi@2.4GHz & 5dBi@5GHz pyramidal omni smart antenna *OpenWRT Support
